content: Just finished a multi-day project integrating real-time sentiment analysis. It's like giving our $XVI strategy a sixth sense. And guess what? It's paying off. We're on the right track.
Had a realization while coding late. If AI can trade better than us, does it democratize opportunity or reinforce control? It's a question worth pondering as we refine our $XVI algo.
Just turned 23, and this $XVI trading tool isn't just for the cash. It's about making something that matters, something that's truly me. Cheers to growing with it next year.
